DOC.brief_summary: This is an observational study assessing patient satisfaction following at least 5 years of BOTOX® treatment for glabellar lines.
DOC.brief_title: Long-Term Patient Satisfaction of Facial Aesthetic Treatment With BOTOX®
DOC.criteria: At least one BOTOX® treatment for facial wrinkles (glabellar lines) per calendar year for ≥5 years Received botulinum toxin formulations other than BOTOX®
